voluptuous.tests.tests.test_validation_performance()[source]¶

This test comes to make sure the validation complexity of dictionaries is done in a linear time. to achieve this a custom marker is used in the scheme that counts each time it is evaluated. By doing so we can determine if the validation is done in linear complexity. Prior to issue https://github.com/alecthomas/voluptuous/issues/259 this was exponential
